abstract_ssm: This collection consists of papers pertaining to a survey commissioned for Ohrbach's department store of New York City, including preliminary planning maps, subway and bus use studies, location map of retail stores, zoning requirements, a photograph of the corner of Sands Street, and alteration costs for an undisclosed building on Fulton Street.
